  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nUser requested detailed risk analysis for BTC, ETH, and XRP with focus on XRP selling strategy. Manus provided comprehensive risk assessment including scores (XRP: 7.15, BTC: 6.20, ETH: 5.75), timeline with Fed decision as critical event, and phased exit recommendations. Subsequently created and deployed interactive website with dashboard visualizations to present analysis findings.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nUser needed decision support for cryptocurrency portfolio management, specifically timing XRP exits around key market events like Fed rate decisions. Requested both analytical depth and accessible presentation format.\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nGenerated comprehensive cryptocurrency risk analysis with scenario modeling, probability assessments, and strategic recommendations. Built and deployed interactive web dashboard with real-time visualizations, navigation tabs, and decision support tools.\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [analysis] Cryptocurrency Risk Assessment — Detailed risk scores, scenario analysis, and strategic recommendations for BTC/ETH/XRP\n- [web_application] Interactive Risk Dashboard — Live website with data visualizations, charts, and navigation for crypto risk analysis\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Identified XRP as highest risk asset (7.15/10) due to extreme overbought conditions\n- Recommended immediate 10% XRP reduction with phased exit strategy\n- Targeted 60-70% position reduction over 6-8 week timeline\n- Created web dashboard for better decision support accessibility\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Comprehensive risk scoring methodology\n- Interactive visualization enhanced understanding\n- Web deployment successful\nDiscoveries:\n\n- XRP showing extreme RSI overbought signals requiring immediate action\n- Fed decision timing critical for exit strategy\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- Will Fed maintain hawkish stance affecting crypto markets?\n- How will XRP ETF decision impact volatility patterns?\n- Should exit strategy be more aggressive given technical indicators?\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- Monitor Fed meeting outcomes on July 30\n- Execute phased XRP reduction starting with 10%\n- Track dashboard metrics for strategy adjustments\n- Reassess risk scores based on market reactions\n---\nUID: zmUhvvY3yzvNjTB2WKZyVy | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0157\n"
